messages.subject: Five Real Princesses Too Badass for Disney Movies
messages.msgSnippet: Not for the very young nor the faint of heart, but an article at Cracked.com called 5 Real Princesses Too Badass for Disney Movies
messages.messageBody:
Not for the very young nor the faint of heart, but an article at Cracked.com called
5 Real Princesses Too Badass for Disney Movies

http://www.cracked.com/article_19478_5-real-princesses-too-badass-disney-movies.html

Examples from France, India, China, Sparta and Galatia.
Trivia connections galore, but sex and violence in some of them.

Those of you with older kids who appreciate random peeks into history might like this, or those of you who are newer to unschooling and haven't yet seen how random dips into trivia can touch all of the past, present and future might want to practice on that stuff.

Sandra
